[Source](http://staroversky.com/blog/gamification-frameworks-and-concepts-visual-summary)

### [Ivan Staroversky's visual summary of all lectures.](http://staroversky.com/blog/gamification-frameworks-and-concepts-visual-summary) 

- Available as searchable PDF (cost $10) and PNG formats. Created using [MindNode for Mac](http://mindnode.com).

## [Christoph Steindl](https://www.coursera.org/user/i/a23d5e4c9c170b0cb9aac72f2fa265c5)'s course notes on video lectures: 

[Source](http://www.catalysts.cc/wissensspritze/gamification/) in [Freemind file format]( http://freemind.sourceforge.net)

